text: Hi! Sorry for not answering earlier, i was busy last Friday and I thought that answering on weekend was a bit in appropriate.
The way the course is made we learn the general bases of vfx and by 3rd year we can choose an expectation.

At the beginning of the year i was considering environmental artist, but a bit than a mont ago I started to consider generalist. I like to do a bit of everything. 
Right now we’re working on 3D pipeline; we’ve to create an improbable invention, model it all in Maya and texture it and integrate it on a footage that we’ve to shoot.
